#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.flatmap.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.flatmap"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:1 of
msgid ""
"Apply the given function to each row and then flatten results. Use this "
"method if your transformation returns multiple rows for each input row."
msgstr ""
"对每一行应用给定的函数，然后将结果展平。如果您的转换对每个输入行返回多个"
"行，请使用此方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:4 of
msgid ""
"This function applies a transformation to each row of the DataFrame, "
"where the transformation can return zero or multiple values, effectively "
"flattening Python generators, list-like collections, and DataFrames."
msgstr ""
"此函数对 DataFrame 的每一行应用一个转换，该转换可以返回零个或多个值，有效"
"地将 Python 生成器、类列表集合和 DataFrame 展平。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:7 of
msgid ""
"Function to apply to each row of the DataFrame. It should accept a Series"
" (or an array if `raw=True`) representing a row and return a list or "
"iterable of values."
msgstr ""
"应用于 DataFrame 每一行的函数。它应接受一个表示行的 Series（如果 `raw="
"True` 则为数组）并返回一个值的列表或可迭代对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:10 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrame."
msgstr "指定返回的 DataFrame 的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:12 of
msgid ""
"Determines if the row is passed as a Series or as a numpy array:  * "
"``False`` : passes each row as a Series to the function. * ``True`` : the"
" passed function will receive numpy array objects instead."
msgstr ""
"确定行是以 Series 还是 numpy 数组的形式传递：  * ``False`` : 将每一行作为"
" Series 传递给函数。 * ``True`` : 传递的函数将接收到 numpy 数组对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:12 of
msgid "Determines if the row is passed as a Series or as a numpy array:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:14 of
msgid "``False`` : passes each row as a Series to the function."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:15 of
msgid "``True`` : the passed function will receive numpy array objects instead."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:17 of
msgid "Positional arguments to pass to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的位置参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:19 of
msgid "Additional keyword arguments to pass as keywords arguments to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的其他关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:21 of
msgid "Return DataFrame with specified `dtypes`."
msgstr "返回指定 `dtypes` 的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:25 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.df_flatmap:26 of
msgid ""
"The ``func`` must return an iterable of values for each input row. The "
"index of the resulting DataFrame will be repeated based on the number of "
"output rows generated by `func`."
msgstr ""
"``func`` 必须为每个输入行返回一个可迭代的值。生成的 DataFrame 的索引将"
"根据 `func` 生成的输出行数重复。"

